calcDelta

protected void calcDelta(Appendable _out,
                         Policy_mxJPO.Signature _oldSignature)
                  throws IOException
Calculates the delta between the old signature and this signature. If for the old signature a branch is defined and for the new signature no branch, an error is thrown.

Parameters:
_out - appendable instance where the delta must be append
_oldSignature - old signature to compare
Throws:
IOException - if the delta could not appended
